To watch his part in action and listen to the interview, skip ahead to the 33-minute mark.</p>

<p>Click <a href="http://bit.ly/1oVXvaw"><strong>HERE</strong></a> to download <strong>NoMrBond</strong>'s F100 Jet Engine.</p>

<p>If you’d like to have a chat <strong>Tanuki</strong> about your add-on or part, leave a PM for us at <a href="http://bit.ly/1knMaSg"><strong>KSP-TV</strong></a>.</p>

<p><strong>Modding Mondays</strong> will return to its regular format next week.</p>
